spec_data.Name: php-LightweightPicasaAPI
spec_data.Description:
PHP wrapper for Google's Picasa Data API, which is implemented using
Atom feeds in XML.  The package is meant to make it easy for PHP
developers to integrate their own applications with Picasa.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 07:14:29 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: A lightweight API for Picasa in PHP
